methods.asRowSet:
Get an RowSet representation of this RowSequence.

:return: (io.deephaven.engine.v2.utils.RowSet) An RowSet representation for the same row keys in the same order
methods.fillRowKeyChunk:
Fill the supplied WritableLongChunk with individual row keys from this RowSequence.
 
 The chunk's capacity is assumed to be big enough.

:param chunkToFill: (io.deephaven.engine.chunk.WritableLongChunk<? extendsio.deephaven.engine.chunk.Attributes.RowKeys>) - A chunk to fill with individual row keys
methods.fillRowKeyRangesChunk:
Fill the supplied WritableLongChunk with row key ranges from this RowSequence.
 
 The chunk's capacity is assumed to be big enough.

:param chunkToFill: (io.deephaven.engine.chunk.WritableLongChunk<io.deephaven.engine.chunk.Attributes.OrderedRowKeyRanges>) - A chunk to fill with row key ranges
methods.firstRowKey:
Get the first row key in this RowSequence.

:return: (long) The first row key, or RowSet.NULL_ROW_KEY if there is none.
methods.isEmpty:
True if the size of this RowSequence is zero.

:return: (boolean) True if there are no elements in this RowSequence.
methods.lastRowKey:
Get the last row key in this RowSequence.

:return: (long) The last row key, or RowSet.NULL_ROW_KEY if there is none.
methods.size:
Get the number of row keys in this RowSequence.

:return: (long) The size, in [0, Long.MAX_VALUE]
